reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute for 8 year olds Big Kid Bedroom
reviews.reviewText: My daughter got a new bed for Christmas- no more bunk beds- and she needed nightstands and lamps so I went with these because they had chargers and plug ins. Super easy to put together, so easy in fact I did it alone while watching a movie lol and had fun! They fit perfectly in her room and though these pictures are after having them a couple days, they are stable and big enough to hold what she needs. 5 stars! Sorry pics looks a little cluttered- she’s using them at the moment 😅.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute night stands but boy they are smaller then I thought
reviews.reviewText: These are pretty small first of all. I didn’t like them as my night stand so I used them in my living room and they worked perfectly! Easy to assemble.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy assembly, cute, smaller than expected
reviews.reviewText: These are really cute! I love that the frames are metal and sturdy. The tops and drawer fronts are particle board but seem pretty strong. The drawer itself is a collapsible canvas (like the cubby cubes). The cord is long and the charging panel is very convenient!They're smaller than I expected, but serve their purpose.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love these nightstands, they are absolutely perfect. They’re sturdy and the fabric drawer is pretty spacious. Great purchase and amazing value for 2! I definitely recommend. Oh and it was super easy to assemble- that’s always a plus :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is great!
reviews.reviewText: It was easy to put together and I love that I can charge my phone, my switch, and have my usb light on at night. The drawer is made of a fabric with a cardboard bottom rather than all wood but it still holds my stuff well! And comes with 2 tables for the price of 1, sign me up! I am happy with them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not worth the cost
reviews.reviewText: Product is a little smaller than I assumed but that is my fault. Instructions were simple but product was missing two peg screws and the drawer is not wooden throughout, only the front panel is wooden.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy assembly and perfect for spare room.
reviews.reviewText: Went together easy and although not the best quality it’s perfect for a spare bedroom.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars These are convenient
reviews.reviewText: These are super cute and convenient. It was also super simple to put together. They are small but that was ok with me. Don’t expect them to look fancy or anything but they are good for the price.
